videos.description: The Golden Eagles' punt attempt goes terribly wrong as an offensive lineman is plunked with the snap, causing a fumble that is recovered by Auburn.
videos.headline: Southern Mississippi's botched punt leads to turnover

videos.description: Tigers quarterback Jarrett Stidham gets whacked as he airs out a 46-yard touchdown pass to Seth Williams, who easily wins the jump ball.
videos.headline: Auburn WR hauls in 46-yard jump ball TD

videos.description: Southern Mississippi quarterback Jack Abraham airmails a deep ball that is picked off by Auburn defensive back Jeremiah Dinson.
videos.headline: Golden Eagles QB airmails interception

videos.description: Tigers wide receiver Anthony Schwartz takes the jet sweep handoff to the edge for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Auburn jet sweep goes for an easy 6

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham throws a deep ball to Darius Slayton for a 53-yard gain, that is followed up by a Chandler Cox 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Auburn's 53-yard catch sets them up for 2-yard score
